  dialogue:
  - What are the fish I caught doing here?
  - They began dying some time after you brought them to the island.
  - Did you keep them in water?
  - Shut up and listen, lad.
  - "They started rotting immediately after. No time to butcher them.\r"
  - You have to go out fishing again.
  - I'm not here to fish, sir. In fact, I would rather limit my time out their on
    the ocean.
  - You should know this already. Are you trying to fuck with me, sir?
  - Watch your tone with me, lad!
  - You better be grateful you even get this opportunity.
  - Now get fishing!
